A '''footjob''' is a [[non-penetrative sex|non-penetrative]] [[sexual practice]] with the [[foot|feet]] that involves one's feet being rubbed on a partner in order to induce sexual excitement, stimulation or [[orgasm]].<ref>{{cite book|title=My Other Self: Sexual Fantasies, Fetishes and Kink|author=Angela Lewis|publisher=The Great American Publishing Society|page=18}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=The Penthouse Erotic Video Guide|author=Eric Danville|publisher=[[Grand Central Publishing]]|isbn=0-446-61293-6|page=263}}</ref> In some cases it can be part of a [[foot fetish]].<ref name=illfootsex>Bruckner, A. (2010). ''Illustrated Foot Sex: Footjobs & Foot Fetishism''. Brian Phillippe.</ref> Footjobs are most often performed on males, with one partner using their feet or toes to stroke or rub the other partner's genital area. ''Footjob'' may also refer to the practice of using one's feet or toes to caress a female partner's [[breasts]] or [[vulva]].<ref>{{cite book|title=The Enlightened Sex Manual|author=David Deida|isbn=1-59179-585-0|publisher=Sounds True, Inc.|year=2007|page=123}}</ref>

